02/14/2023

Note: Open Rproj first, then script. To easily use relative paths, click the down button next to knit and then click Knit Directory > Project Directory. This should make loading and saving files much easier.

7. Differential gene expression analysis for TreeSplit (D v T1 v T2)

Make DGE object

treatmentinfo_treesplit <- filter(treatmentinfo, treesplit!="")
gcount_treesplit <- gcount[,treatmentinfo_treesplit$sample]
DGEdat <- DGEList(counts=as.matrix(gcount_treesplit), samples=treatmentinfo_treesplit,
                  group=treatmentinfo_treesplit$treesplit)

2. Pre-filtering

keep <- rowSums(cpm(gcount_treesplit) > 3.33) >= 2
table(keep)
DGEdat <- DGEdat[keep, , keep.lib.sizes=FALSE]
DGEdat <- calcNormFactors(DGEdat)
DGEdat$samples

Creating the design matrix

TreeSplit=factor(DGEdat$samples$treesplit, levels = c("D", "T1", "T2"))
design <- model.matrix(~0+TreeSplit)
colnames(design) <- levels(TreeSplit)
head(design); dim(design)

Estimate dispersion and fit a glmQL model

DGEdat <- estimateDisp(DGEdat, design, robust=TRUE)
fit <- glmQLFit(DGEdat, design, robust=TRUE)
head(fit$coefficients)
plotQLDisp(fit)

Set contrasts

test.T1 <- makeContrasts(T1 - D, levels = design)
res.T1 <- glmQLFTest(fit, contrast = test.T1)
topTags(res.T1)
T1.de <- decideTestsDGE(res.T1, adjust.method="BH", p.value=0.05, lfc=2)
summary(T1.de)
DEGtable.T1_D <- res.T1$table[T1.de!=0,]
DEGtable.T1_D$contrast <- "T1vD"
DEGtable.T1_D$gene_id  <- rownames(DEGtable.T1_D)
rownames(DEGtable.T1_D) <- NULL

test.T2 <- makeContrasts(T2 - D, levels = design)
res.T2 <- glmQLFTest(fit, contrast = test.T2)
topTags(res.T2)
T2.de <- decideTestsDGE(res.T2, adjust.method="BH", p.value=0.05, lfc=2)
summary(T2.de)
DEGtable.T2_D <- res.T2$table[T2.de!=0,]
DEGtable.T2_D$contrast <- "T2vD"
DEGtable.T2_D$gene_id  <- rownames(DEGtable.T2_D)
rownames(DEGtable.T2_D) <- NULL

test.12 <- makeContrasts(T1 - T2, levels = design)
res.12 <- glmQLFTest(fit, contrast = test.12)
topTags(res.12)
newT1.de <- decideTestsDGE(res.12, adjust.method = "BH", p.value = 0.05, lfc=2)
summary(newT1.de)
DEGtable.T1_T2 <- res.12$table[newT1.de!=0,]
DEGtable.T1_T2$contrast <- "T1vT2"
DEGtable.T1_T2$gene_id  <- rownames(DEGtable.T1_T2)
rownames(DEGtable.T1_T2) <- NULL

DEGtable.all <- bind_rows(DEGtable.T1_D, DEGtable.T2_D, DEGtable.T1_T2)
DEGtable.all <- cbind(DEGtable.all, cluster=ifelse(DEGtable.all$logFC>0, "Up", "Down"))
write_csv(DEGtable.all[,c(6,1:5,7)], "Output/Supplementary_table_treesplit_DEGs.csv", col_names = T)
